r.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20stress%20it%20was%20causing%20me%20until%20that%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20had%20to%20commute%20to%20Atlanta%20every%20month%20for%20work.%20I%20could%20leave%20my%20house%20and%20be%20at%20my%20airport%20gate%20within%2020%20minutes.%20I've%20never%20flown%20private%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20imagine%20it's%20much%20better%20than%20that.%20While%20I%20could%20fly%20direct%20to%20Atlanta%20or%20Washington%20D.C.%2C%20most%20other%20flights%20had%20connections%2C%20which%20was%20a%20change%20from%20Atlanta%2C%20where%20I%20could%20fly%20direct%20anywhere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c49f9ca-7145-42c3-8ffe-fb4fd22a499a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20boosted%20my%20career%2C%20too%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20very%20good%20at%20what%20I%20do%2C%20but%20there%20was%20much%20more%20competition%20in%20Atlanta.%20Although%20I%20had%20a%20good%20network%2C%20it%20wasn't%20as%20deep%20as%20the%20networks%20of%20people%20who%20had%20family%20ties%20in%20Atlanta%20or%20went%20to%20college%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20moved%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20a%20wonderful%20network.%20It's%20not%20just%20because%20I%20grew%20up%20here%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20because%2C%20in%20a%20smaller%20city%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20bigger%20impact.%20I%20have%20the%20mayor's%20number%2C%20and%20I'm%20confident%20I%20could%20get%20the%20governor%20on%20the%20phone%20if%20needed.%20Because%20of%20networking%20and%20less%20competition%2C%20my%20business%20has%20flourished.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20in%20Baton%20Rouge%20isn't%20big%20city%20life%2C%20but%20it%20has%20everything%20I%20need.%20Sure%2C%20I%20might%20need%20to%20search%20more%2C%20but%20I%20can%20still%20go%20to%20the%20symphony%2C%20meet%20friends%20for%20drinks%2C%20and%20make%20professional%20connections%2C%20all%20without%20the%20stress%20I%20had%20in%20A