e%20in%20teaching%20machines%20how%20to%20think%20and%20speak%20like%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong%20told%20AdExchanger%20that%20Reddit's%20introduction%20of%20AI%20translation%20features%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20helped%20the%20company%20grow%20at%20an%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%20rate%26quot%3B%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Reddit%20announced%20the%20expansion%20of%20an%20AI-powered%20translation%20feature%20that%20lets%20users%20translate%20Reddit%20posts%20and%20comments%20into%20different%20languages.%20The%20expansion%20covered%20more%20than%2035%20countries%2C%20including%20Brazil%2C%20Spain%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20and%20countries%20throughout%20Latin%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20made%20our%20core%20product%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20find%20a%20home%20on%20Reddit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong%20also%20said%20that%20Reddit%20plans%20to%20use%20AI%20on%20its%20advertising%20platform%20to%20create%20more%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20variants%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmake%20things%20more%20Reddity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bought%20a%20company%2C%20Memorable%20AI%2C%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20told%20AdExchanger.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunity%20for%20our%20AI%20application.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20acquired%20Memorable%20AI%2C%20an%20AI-based%20advertisement%20company%2C%20in%20August%202024.%20Reddit%20said%20that%20the%20acquisition%20would%20give%20Reddit%20advertisers%20access%20to%20Memorable's%20%26quot%3Bbest-in-class%26quot%3B%20tools%20for%20advancing%20advertising%20campaigns%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-comments-ai-training-models-google-openai-jen-wong-huffman-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737212627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678963a38bb735b73550c2f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-comments-ai-training-models-google-openai-jen-wong-huffman-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reddit%20signed%20deals%20with%20Google%20and%20OpenAI%20last%20year%20that%20allows%20the%20tech%20companies%20to%20train%20their%20AI%20models%20on%20Reddit%20content.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-comments-ai-training-models-google-openai-jen-wong-huffman-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Court%20Allowed%20Sex%20Crimes%20Accused%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20To%20Watch%20Assault%20Clips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20accused%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20obscene%20video%20scandal%20--%20former%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20who%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20ex-Prime%20Minister%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20was%20allowed%20by%20a%20special%20court%20on%20Saturday%20to%20view%20alleged%20videos%20of%20sexual%20assaults%20involving%20the%20victim%20in%20a%20closed%20court%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Special%20Court%20for%20MLAs%2FMPs%20granted%20permission%20for%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20his%20counsel%2C%20a%20technical%20team%2C%20and%20the%20Special%20Public%20Prosecutor%20(SPP)%20to%20review%20the%20confidential%20videos%20retrieved%20from%20the%20personal%20cellphone%20of%20the%20former%20MP's%20driver%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20closely%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20court%20from%20the%20Central%20Prison%20in%20Parappana%20Agrahara%20following%20the%20order%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna's%20counsel%2C%20submitted%20a%20request%20to%20the%20court%20to%20restrict%20the%20media%20from%20publishing%20news%20about%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20declined%2C%20stating%20it%20could%20not%20issue%20such%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20further%20requested%20an%20adjournment%20for%20the%20confidential%20viewing%20of%20the%20data%2C%20citing%20the%20absence%20of%20technical%20experts.%20The%20court%20expressed%20displeasure%2C%20noting%20that%20such%20requests%20appeared%20to%20be%20delay%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20objection%20if%20the%20counsel%20files%20an%20application%20requesting%20a%20female%20judge%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Mr%20Revanna%C2%A0and%20the%20others%20viewed%20the%20confidential%20private%20data%2C%20which%20included%20the%20alleged%20sex%20videos%20retrieved%20from%20the%20driver's%20personal%20cellphone%2C%20in%20the%20closed%20court%20hall.%20The%20driver%20had%20worked%20for%20Mr%20Revanna%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Revanna%20earlier%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20with%20the%20High%20Court%20seeking%20the%20production%20of%20documents%20and%20electronic%20evidence%20collected%20by%20investigators%20from%20his%20driver's%20personal%20mobile%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20here%20is%20obscene%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20limit%20to%20obscenity.%20The%20court%20cannot%20provide%20data%20about%20other%20women.%20You%20are%20trying%20to%20turn%20back%20the%20clock%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20the%20High%20Court%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20looking%20into%20the%20sex%20video%20scandal%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20law%20cannot%20be%20bent%20just%20because%20the%20matter%20pertains%20to%20Prajwal%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20M%20Nagaprasanna%20made%20the%20statement%20while%20hearing%20the%20petition%20by%20Prajwal%20seeking%20to%20quash%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20against%20him.%20Mr%20Revanna%20specifically%20requested%20access%20to%20all%20data%20from%20the%20mobile%20phone.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20clarified%20that%20only%20data%20relevant%20to%20the%20specific%20case%20could%20be%20inspected%2C%20and%20access%20to%20data%20involving%20other%20women%20would%20not%20be%20permitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20breach%20of%20privacy%20of%20other%20women%20should%20be%20done.%20Forget%20about%20others.%20The%20victims'%20images%20are%20here%2C%20they%20are%20obscene%20to%20the%20core.%20Just%20because%20it%20is%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20the%20law%20cannot%20be%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20had%20remarked%20orally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20submitted%20that%20the%20phone%20was%20thoroughly%20examined%20by%20the%20investigators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20investigating%20officer%20has%20examined%20the%20material.%20The%20electronic%20evidence%20and%20records%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20evidence.%20The%20prosecution%20objected%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20entire%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bench%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20petitioner%20wants%20data%20concerning%20other%20women%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20cases%20pertaining%20to%20the%20privacy%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20the%20court%20can%20only%20arrange%20for%20inspection.%20Any%20means%20of%20inspection%20could%20be%20provided%2C%20but%20it%20can't%20be%20provided%20to%20you%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20pen%20drive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20observed%20that%20barring%20the%20case%20in%20which%20a%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%2C%20Mr%20Revanna%20cannot%20ask%20for%20data%20on%20other%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner's%20counsel%20maintained%20that%20it%20will%20cause%20serious%20prejudice%20to%20him%20and%20he%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20inspect%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20stated%20orally%20that%20copies%20will%20be%20provided%20protecting%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20women%20and%20disposed%20of%20Mr%20Revanna's%20petition%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20has%20charged%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20under%20Sections%20354%20(A)%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354%20(B)%20(assault%20or%20use%20of%20criminal%20force%20on%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20her)%2C%20354%20(C)%20(act%20of%20watching%20or%20capturing%20a%20woman's%20image%20while%20she%20is%20engaging%20in%20a%20private%20act)%2C%20376%20(2)%20(N)%20(aggravated%20form%20of%20rape%20committed%20by%20police%20officers%20and%20other%20public%20servants%20in%20charge%2C%20repeatedly%20raping%20same%20woman)%2C%20376%20(2)%20(K)%20(being%20in%20position%20of%20control%20or%20dominance%20over%20a%20woman%2C%20committing%20rape)%2C%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%20201%20(causing%20disappearance%20of%20evidence)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Section%2066%20(E)%20of%20the%20IT%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20investigating%20the%20sexual%20assault%20video%20case%20involving%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20submitted%20the%201%2C691-page%20charge%20sheet%20to%20the%20Special%20Court%20for%20MLAs%2FMPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charge%20sheet%20had%20mentioned%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20raped%20at%20gunpoint.%20The%20video%20was%20made%20of%20the%20rape%20incident%20and%20the%20victim%20was%20repeatedly%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20threatened%20her%20with%20making%20her%20videos%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20victim%20had%20not%20dared%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20out%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737212220000%2C%22visual%2