amage%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20termed%20the%20California%20wildfires%20and%20particularly%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20inferno%20as%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20predictable%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20pointed%20at%20the%20poorly%20understood%20idea%20of%20safety%20amid%20the%20climate%20crisis%20as%20%26quot%3Bwealth%20and%20affluence%26quot%3B%20alone%20cannot%20save%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bweird%20thing%20about%20climate%20change%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20phenomenon%20that%20manifests%20locally%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20Jnanpith%20Award%20recipient%20and%20winner%20of%20the%20Erasmus%20Prize%20for%20his%20writings%20on%20the%20planetary%20crisis%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20California%20case%20was%20completely%20predictable%20as%20it%20was%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20geographical%20zone%20where%20it's%20bound%20to%20have%20catastrophes.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20exactly%20that%20kind%20of%20climate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20a%20desert.%20The%20problem%20with%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20particular%20is%20all%20its%20water%20comes%20from%20very%20distant%20sources%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20institutional%20corruption%20built%20into%20it.%20A%20couple%20of%20billionaires%20have%20diverted%20a%20lot%20of%20water%20to%20their%20farms%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20will%20see%20in%20all%20these%20disasters%20that%20are%20playing%20out%20across%20the%20planet%20is%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20an%20intensifier.%20But%20you%20can't%20understand%20any%20of%20them%20without%20understanding%20the%20localism%20of%20it.%20Because%20this%20is%20the%20weird%20thing%20about%20climate%20change%20-%20it's%20a%20global%20phenomenon%20that%20manifests%20locally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20celebrated%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20people%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20how%20climate%20change%20is%20interacting%20with%20local%20patterns%20of%20settlement%2C%20and%20local%20patterns%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20just%20take%20the%20case%20of%20Chennai%2C%20for%20example%2C%20which%20has%20had%20these%20rain%20bomb%20events%2C%20repeatedly%2C%20the%20problem%20there%20is%20they%20have%20built%20over%20an%20entire%20floodplain.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20have%20these%20very%20unsustainable%20patterns%20of%20urban%20development%20around%20Mumbai.%20And%20the%20same%20is%20true%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%20They%20should%20not%20be%20building%20along%20mountains%20where%20it's%20known%20that%20fires%20will%20happen%2C%20and%20they%20have%20happened%20repeatedly%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20firefighters%20continued%20their%20efforts%20to%20snuff%20out%20hotspots%20over%20the%2040%2C000%20acres%20that%20have%20been%20burned%20--%20an%20area%20almost%20as%20big%20as%20Washington%20DC.%20All%20over%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20the%20acclaim%20for%20first%20responders%20stood%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20political%20bickering%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20Republicans%20across%20the%20US%20line%20up%20behind%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20as%20he%20bashes%20California's%20Democratic%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Eric%20Braeden%2C%20a%20mainstay%20of%20US%20daytime%20soap%20opera%20'The%20Young%20and%20the%20Restless%2C'%20on%20Thursday%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20issue.%20US%20tennis%20great%20Pam%20Shriver%20appealed%20for%20the%20return%20of%20trophies%20stolen%20with%20her%20car%20after%20she%20evacuated%20her%20luxury%20home.%20Dozens%20of%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20disaster%2C%20with%20several%20charged%20for%20looting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%20said%20the%20US%20could%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20again%20aft