d%20to%20attract%20millions%20of%20devotees%2C%20with%20the%20event%20continuing%20until%20February%2026%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20parallel%20effort%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20operations%20and%20the%20safety%20of%20pilgrims%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20will%20inspect%20the%20ongoing%20arrangements%20and%20safety%20measures%20in%20place%20for%20the%20vast%20influx%20of%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday%20marks%20the%20sixth%20day%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20with%20a%20massive%20crowd%20expected%20to%20gather%20for%20the%20auspicious%20Amrit%20Snan.%20This%20ritual%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20bathing%20festivals%20of%20the%20event%2C%20with%20devotees%20bathing%20in%20the%20Sangam%20to%20cleanse%20themselves%20spiritually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Amrit%20Snan%20was%20held%20on%20January%2014%2C%20coinciding%20with%20Makar%20Sankranti%2C%20and%20the%20second%20will%20take%20place%20on%20January%2029%20for%20Mauni%20Amavasya%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20third%20on%20February%203%20for%20Basant%20Panchami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20safety%20during%20the%20sacred%20baths%2C%20a%20specialised%20team%20of%20220%20expert%20divers%20from%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20and%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(SDRF)%20has%20been%20deployed.%20They%20operate%20in%20shifts%2C%20supported%20by%20700%20boats%20to%20ensure%20vigilance%20at%20all%20times.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20divers%2C%20security%20personnel%20from%20the%20NDRF%2C%20SDRF%2C%20PAC%2C%20water%20police%2C%20and%20healthcare%20teams%20are%20working%20together%20to%20keep%20the%20event%20running%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20accommodate%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20visitors%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20State%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%20(UPSTDC)%20has%20enhanced%20lodging%20options.%20A%20deluxe%20300-bed%20dormitory%20has%20been%20established%20within%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20a