0%9CThe%20paver%20tile%20has%20more%20strength%20than%20a%20normal%20interlock%20made%20of%20concrete.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20our%20USPs%20(Unique%20Selling%20Point).%20There%20is%20also%20no%20issue%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20or%20rusting%2C%20which%20is%20common%20in%20metal%20benches.%20If%20anything%20happens%20to%20the%20recycled%20material%2C%20we%20can%20recycle%20it%20again.%20As%20these%20are%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20they%20are%20durable%20and%20protected%20from%20termite%20damage%2C%20unlike%20wooden%20furniture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20interlock%20paver%20tiles%20and%20public%20benches%20have%20already%20been%20installed%20in%20several%20malls%20and%20metro%20stations%20across%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20friends%20have%20partnered%20with%20LuLu%20Group%2C%20HiLITE%20group%2C%20Cochin%20Smart%20Mission%20Limited%20(CSML)%2C%20Malabar%20Group%2C%20Centre%20Square%20Mall%20Kochi%2C%20Kochi%20Metro%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20into%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20the%20company%20claims%20to%20have%20saved%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste%20from%20polluting%20landfills%20and%20oceans.%20Siddharth%20mentions%20that%20their%20mission%20is%20to%20declutter%20one%20million%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20waste%20in%20Kerala%20as%20part%20of%20their%20ongoing%20campaign%2C%20%23Declutter.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20we%20have%20successfully%20transformed%203%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-credit-recycle-mumbai-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%20items%20%3C%2Fa%3Einto%20useful%20products%20like%20public%20benches.%20While%203%2C000%20is%20just%20a%20small%20step%20toward%20the%20one-million%20goal%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20continuing%20our%20efforts%20until%20every%20piece%20of%20waste%20is%20addressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20also%20explored%20the%20B2B%20section%20to%20ensure%20the%20traceability%20and%20accountability%20of%20the%20plastic.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20focus%20on%20selling%20directly%20to%20the%20consumer%20because%2C%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20our%20accountability%20is%20lost.%20If%20something%20breaks%2C%20consumers%20will%20throw%20the%20furniture%20away%20and%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20back%20to%20us.%20With%20B2B%2C%20we%20can%20ensure%20proper%20traceability%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Alvin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDDemObyPZD9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDDemObyPZD9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fre