erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-05-at-18.10.21-1-1736084210.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETejas%20is%20working%20to%20solve%20education%20problems%20and%20environmental%20issues%20through%20his%20initiative.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20volunteer%20contributes%20meaningfully%2C%20whether%20by%20collecting%20textile%20waste%2C%20connecting%20with%20local%20schools%2C%20or%20distributing%20eco-friendly%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20three%20goals%20in%20mind%20when%20we%20started%3A%20to%20help%20children%20attend%20school%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299084%2Fdesigner-upcycles-scrap-fabric-into-trendy-clothes-bags-lets-save-as-anshika-yadav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20textile%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20empower%20marginalised%20and%20disabled%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20goal%20has%20already%20seen%20incredible%20results.%20Through%20our%20surveys%2C%20we%20found%20that%20attendance%20rates%20in%20government%20schools%20where%20we%20distributed%20the%20bags%20increased%20by%2034%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20goes%20beyond%20just%20improving%20attendance.%20The%20team%20has%20distributed%20over%203%2C000%20bags%2C%20saving%20over%2070%20million%20litres%20of%20water%2C%20preventing%2058%2C000%20kg%20of%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20upcycling%20more%20than%203%2C600%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste.%20These%20figures%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20numbers%2C%20they%20represent%20real%20change%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20hope%20for%20those%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%20the%20mission%3A%20Threads4Good%E2%80%99s%20plans%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%