hildren%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20where%20their%20next%20meal%20will%20come%20from.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20of%20Tejas%2C%20his%20volunteers%2C%20and%20the%20marginalised%20workers%2C%20Threads4Good%20has%20blossomed%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20issues%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383933%2Fnarayanpur-high-school-environmental-education-sustainability-east-kolkata-wetlands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20and%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20creates%20a%20sense%20of%20dignity%20and%20independence%20for%20those%20who%20have%20been%20excluded%20from%20the%20mainstream%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20teen%20founder%20humbly%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20to%20see%20how%20something%20so%20small%20can%20make%20such%20a%20big%20impact.%20I%20am%20glad%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20the%20initiative%2C%20but%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20when%20I%20saw%20it%20garner%20so%20much%20attention%20among%20students%20and%20their%20parents.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learned%20that%20the%20power%20of%20community%20is%20unstoppable%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20to%20see%20where%20this%20journey%20will%20take%20us%20next.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Tejas%20Pugalia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736911800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-18-at-1.14.21-PM-1_11zon-1736083535.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D395350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20just%2017%2C%20Tejas%20Pugalia%20has%20founded%20Threads4Good%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20provides%20school%20bags%20to%20marginalised%20students%2C%20reduces%20textile%20waste%2C%20and%