tps%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329041%2Fassam-woman-starts-vermicompost-business-after-husband-death-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20fertiliser%20%3C%2Fa%3Edirectly%20to%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhushal%20Singh%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20non-profit%20for%20tree%20conservation%2C%20also%20undertook%20training%20from%20Kavya%20to%20learn%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20vermicomposting.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20buy%20vermicompost%20from%20the%20market%20to%20plant%20our%20saplings%2C%20which%20we%20grow%20on%20largely%20barren%20land.%20These%20young%20plants%20need%20constant%20care%20for%20the%20first%20three%20years%2C%20and%20adding%20compost%20along%20with%20water%20significantly%20aids%20their%20growth.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20purchasing%20compost%20was%20adding%20up%20to%20our%20daily%20expenses.%20So%2C%20making%20our%20own%20compost%20not%20only%20helped%20us%20cut%20fertiliser%20expenses%20but%20also%20sell%20the%20excess%20to%20local%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavya%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20the%20healthcare%20trenches%20to%20agricultural%20fields%20is%20more%20than%20a%20career%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mission.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20restoring%20health%20to%20both%20humans%20and%20the%20planet.%20As%20she%20navigates%20challenges%2C%20cultivates%20change%2C%20and%20impacts%20thousands%2C%20Kavya%20believes%20that%20healing%20can%20start%20from%20the%20soil%20beneath%20our%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20each%20farmer%20trained%2C%20each%20field%20revived%2C%20and%20each%20life%20touched%2C%20our%20work%20offers%20hope%20that%20together%2C%20we%20can%20indeed%20save%20soil%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20save%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Kavya%20Dhobale%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736740658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3